    sa: `Coach reps on their pipeline by inspecting deals through questions rather than giving answers, focusing each session on stalls, missing next steps, and unrealistic close dates, and reinforcing the habits that keep a pipeline healthy between reviews. The goal is a rep who manages their own pipeline well, not one who depends on you to find every problem.`,
